{"tid":2339173,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"★Market Digest】連登紅人麵咪媽發文撐阿里巴巴，阿里巴巴股價就...","createTime":"2020-12-24T12:26:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-24T13:15:50.000Z","uid":19454,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"407ab112df1faf8919976df239f9dd7415dafe79","tid":2339173,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T12:26:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/dlBCWpfyuiPCe0uCQNuWFw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTk2MA--/https://s.yimg.com/uu/api/res/1.2/jYVQumJrhdBqj_LiFVJXhw--~B/aD0xMjAwO3c9MTIwMDthcHBpZD15dGFjaHlvbg--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/market_digest_986/d38c404452c875b17ec4a3f08c6f7e0e\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FdlBCWpfyuiPCe0uCQNuWFw--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTk2MA--%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fuu%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FjYVQumJrhdBqj_LiFVJXhw--~B%2FaD0xMjAwO3c9MTIwMDthcHBpZD15dGFjaHlvbg--%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen%2Fmarket_digest_986%2Fd38c404452c875b17ec4a3f08c6f7e0e&h=aa79e6bf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n連登紅人麵咪媽於今年12月20日在連登討論區以「唉 咪x話我麵仔孤x寒啦 益埋你地班正股投資者啦 強烈推介三隻正股俾你地!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!」為題發文支持ATM（阿里巴巴、騰訊及美團），指出「股王阿里爸爸 250天線不破底 唔好問幾錢入好 瞇埋眼入就得」。<br />\n<br />\n不過，阿里巴巴（9988）今日（24日）卻處於弱勢，一度大跌9％至226.2元，收報228.2元，跌8％，成交額159億元。<br />\n<br />\n事緣中國市場監管總局近日根據舉報，依法對阿里巴巴實施「二選一」等涉嫌壟斷行為立案調查。消息令投資者拋售阿里巴巴股票。<br />\n<br />\n說回麵咪媽的帖文，他亦留言「另一隻股王騰訊 唔好講250天線呀 100天線位都未破過 都係唔好問幾錢入好 瞇埋眼入就得」；「又係股王 美團 就咁睇好似穿哂三條天線位 但睇真D你就會覺得係假穿 依家呢個位入 一個字 sure win呀!!!!!!!!!!!!」<br />\n<br />\n最後他亦補上：「呢三隻股王就當我媽咪哥送俾大家既聖誕禮物啦 merry christmas !!!!!!!!」<br />\n<br />\n事實上，麵咪媽的「聖誕禮物」亦包括騰訊及美團。<br />\n<br />\n製圖／文字：Market Digest<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/news/%E9%80%A3%E7%99%BB%E7%B4%85%E4%BA%BA%E9%BA%B5%E5%92%AA%E5%AA%BD%E7%99%BC%E6%96%87%E6%92%90%E9%98%BF%E9%87%8C%E5%B7%B4%E5%B7%B4-%E9%98%BF%E9%87%8C%E5%B7%B4%E5%B7%B4%E8%82%A1%E5%83%B9%E5%B0%B1-041853229.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.yahoo.com%2Fnews%2F%25E9%2580%25A3%25E7%2599%25BB%25E7%25B4%2585%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E9%25BA%25B5%25E5%2592%25AA%25E5%25AA%25BD%25E7%2599%25BC%25E6%2596%2587%25E6%2592%2590%25E9%2598%25BF%25E9%2587%258C%25E5%25B7%25B4%25E5%25B7%25B4-%25E9%2598%25BF%25E9%2587%258C%25E5%25B7%25B4%25E5%25B7%25B4%25E8%2582%25A1%25E5%2583%25B9%25E5%25B0%25B1-041853229.html&d=z%2FAKp4ZZwI77wMFl%2FSXGt4%2FGH25nCqGTJutLbOxS7Ms%3D&h=b219fdfa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/news/%E9%80%A3%E7%99%BB%E7%B4%85%E4%BA%BA%E9%BA%B5%E5%92%AA%E5%AA%BD%E7%99%BC%E6%96%87%E6%92%90%E9%98%BF%E9%87%8C%E5%B7%B4%E5%B7%B4-%E9%98%BF%E9%87%8C%E5%B7%B4%E5%B7%B4%E8%82%A1%E5%83%B9%E5%B0%B1-041853229.html</a>"},{"pid":"bf6306eb162c0792fa6e258b5f670ecfc7291eee","tid":2339173,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T12:27:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1288fe2c4f1ac29ef7e65d31308e60cda0fcbd8","tid":2339173,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T12:55:37.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\"><strong>股壇至尊<br />\n燈神麵仔<br />\n燈爆股壇<br />\n莫敢不從<br />\n都督不出<br />\n誰與爭鋒<br />\n</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"89d8502f91862024f5eb6863f9bec1d156186d14","tid":2339173,"uid":117947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T13:15:50.000Z","msg":"要問自己點解唔把握機會"}]}